      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZING MATILDA (7) placed two back in a Grade 5 at Gawler then backed that up with a third (22.72) over 395m at Murray Bridge last time. Speedy runner who can find the front with a clear break from out wide. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. PINK POPPY CLUB (5) boasts a strong record this journey with four wins and two minors from nine tries. In the money last time at Angle Park (19.66) in a Other, finishing a 2 length second. Makes strong appeal on best. URANA UNO (8) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth at Mt Gambier, but was among the placings at this track three back. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from on outside draw. Well placed here and can atone this time. NATIONAL GRID (1) was out of placings last time (20.09) at Angle Park in a Other, finishing fifth and beaten 8 lengths. Has four wins already from this draw.",
